The paper describes the design and progress of a journal that publishes articles describing research software, with a focus on improving the quality of the software submitted and providing a mechanism for research software developers to receive credit. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE), as well as cybernetics (cs.CY), programming languages (cs.PL), open access (cs.OH), and digital libraries (cs.DL).
